{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I\u2019ve reached the decision point: the clean path is a dedicated backend audio-estimation service plus a tiny frontend preview calculator, rather than another API round-trip for every slider move. Next I\u2019m checking the existing frontend he...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_28", "text": "I\u2019ve reached the decision point: the clean path is a dedicated backend audio-estimation service plus a tiny frontend preview calculator, rather than another API round-trip for every slider move. Next I\u2019m checking the existing frontend heuristic utilities and the composition/session data shape so the preview math can reuse explicit assumption fields instead of inventing its own hidden constants.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 57, "prompt_index": 72, "prompt_name": "71 \u2014 Audio Length Estimation Heuristics", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T14:07:56-07:00"}
