{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The Compose stack is already up, so I\u2019m using it for the screenshot-backed QA rather than spinning up extra dev servers. I\u2019m reading the browser service setup and then I\u2019ll seed a concrete audio-stage session in the live Postgres so I ca...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_88", "text": "The Compose stack is already up, so I\u2019m using it for the screenshot-backed QA rather than spinning up extra dev servers. I\u2019m reading the browser service setup and then I\u2019ll seed a concrete audio-stage session in the live Postgres so I can capture the estimate card in the actual app.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 167, "prompt_index": 72, "prompt_name": "71 \u2014 Audio Length Estimation Heuristics", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T14:16:29-07:00"}
